sudo journalctl | grep UFW
tail -f /var/log/ufw.log
---

# Best Practices with UFW

1. Always allow SSH before enabling UFW.
2. Use `ufw status numbered` to manage rules more easily.
3. Set a deny-by-default policy.
4. Log and review regularly.
5. Rate limit sensitive services like SSH.
6. Test new rules with `nmap` or `ss` before closing your terminal.
